Greenness, civil environment, and pregnancy outcomes: perspectives with a 
systematic review and meta-analysis.

Lee KJ(1)(2)(3), Moon H(4), Yun HR(4), Park EL(4), Park AR(4), Choi H(5), Hong 
K(6)(7), Lee J(8).

Author information:
(1)Department of Obstetrics and Gynecology, Korea University Medicine, 73, 
