DO-HEALTH: Vitamin D3 - Omega-3 - Home exercise - Healthy aging and longevity 
trial - Design of a multinational clinical trial on healthy aging among European 
seniors.

Bischoff-Ferrari HA(1), de Godoi Rezende Costa Molino C(2), Rival S(2), Vellas 
B(3), Rizzoli R(4), Kressig RW(5), Kanis JA(6), Manson JE(7), Dawson-Hughes 
